entries.journal_entry_description: An Imperial transport was shot down on Rori. Investigate.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Investigate an Imperial transport that was shot down on Rori.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Complete the mission that was interrupted when the transport was shot down.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Now we send a message to those who would attack an Imperial ship. The squad of Rebel Commandos who shot down the transport have been located. Eliminate them!
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Captain Thrawn at the Emperor's Retreat
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Deliver the recovered Ballistics report to Major Geg Winthazen.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Retrieve a prototype rocket from Seldair Keeloo. The meeting location with Seldair was not mentioned in the mission data, but it is known that he will be in Narmle.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Get the prototype rocket back from the thieves who stole it. One of the thieves will be carrying it. All Seldair knew was that they have a hideout somewhere outside of Narmle.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Recover the mission data from the Imperial operatives that were on the transport.
